          <p>Stay up to date with all upcoming UFC events.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature card">
          <div class="icon">ğŸ‘Š</div>
          <h3>Fighter Database</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive fighter stats and records.</p>
        </div>

